{"tid":2327606,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"篠原涼子挑戰電視尺度 落實參演Netflix原創劇集演不倫人妻","createTime":"2020-12-16T07:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T16:57:44.000Z","uid":318316,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d548a1c817bbda55e8db4df11a5b9ce40df1958a","tid":2327606,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8uawgQuPwffJ_eDE3T94KJwidy0=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QWNPEOTAXVCZNIWSD7SGQW33Y4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8uawgQuPwffJ_eDE3T94KJwidy0%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQWNPEOTAXVCZNIWSD7SGQW33Y4.jpg&h=599914b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《金魚妻》改編自漫畫家黑澤R的同名漫畫，作品已賣出累積超過220萬本。故事講述主人翁平賀櫻放棄夢想，與一名經營美容院的男子結婚，過着令人羨慕的少奶奶生活。然而，平賀櫻卻受盡丈夫的言語及肉體的暴力對待，當她孤獨一人的時候，內心一直被痛苦包圍。有一日，平賀櫻因為飼養金魚而結識到一名男子，繼而控制不住埋藏已久的慾望，踩過界與男子發生不倫戀。篠原涼子自言從未演過這樣的角色，所以懷着挑戰的心情演戲。劇集由Netflix和Fuji Creative Corporation共同製作，富士電視台監製中野利幸表示：「原作以描寫女性細膩的心情和情慾吸引讀者，但在電視畫面上卻很難原汁原味呈現出來，所以今次與Netflix合作，不用猶豫就能夠挑戰性愛場面，相信會有很出色的化學效應。」暗示涼子將會有超越電視尺度的突破性演出，劇集暫定於明年在Netflix開播。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201210/5YEQEZ6WJRDYROUE4AEJ7GXGLA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201210%2F5YEQEZ6WJRDYROUE4AEJ7GXGLA%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU5j7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=f46065ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201210%2F5YEQEZ6WJRDYROUE4AEJ7GXGLA%2F&h=1ef048e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201210/5YEQEZ6WJRDYROUE4AEJ7GXGLA/</a>"},{"pid":"62e067e80904d2beafe5ae0383b6fb45b9ece368","tid":2327606,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"搵得Netflix當然為求突破啦<img src=\"